Actress Omuhle Gela makes her debut as Nomaswazi on SABC 1’s Uzalo on Monday. Omuhle explained her joy at being a part of the family: ” It’s such an honour working on such a huge production, the cast and crew have been extremely welcoming since day one and that’s made it very easy working on the production as a whole.’’ Nomaswazi wants her rightful place at the table. She wants to lead, she is smart, calculating, and moves stealthily.   For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.